N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 152.11 - Nonresident aliens

State Regulations

Tax Law, ยง 651(g)

The due date for filing a New York State personal
income tax return which is required to be filed for the taxable year by a
nonresident alien individual is the date prescribed for the filing of his or
her Federal income tax return for the taxable year. Notes
